nodes.title: Positive
widgets_values: A highly detailed macro photograph of a majestic futuristic mechanical bird perched on a moss-covered branch in an ancient forest at sunrise. The bird's feathers are constructed from iridescent glass and polished gold, revealing intricate internal gears and glowing blue optical fibers within its body. Its eyes glow softly with an inner light. Dew droplets cling to the metal and glass surfaces of its form, catching the golden morning light filtering through the trees. The background is a soft, magical bokeh of light and forest greens. Cinematic lighting, rich textures, shallow depth of field.
